column5: 1b/1b, 900sq.f., upstairs condo, it's just a 5 minute walk down the boardwalk to the beach, you will like the quiet and cleanliness of the complex with manicured lawn and beautiful tropical landscape. Airbnb quote does include 7% city of Port Aransas hotel tax, Airbnb charges 6% state hotel tax!
